Package: NUIMM
Type: Package
Title: NUIMM: Network-based utility for integrating microbiome and metabolome data
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Bowornpol Nuim [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Bowornpol Nuim <bowornpol@hotmail.com>
Description: A comprehensive R package designed for integrating microbiome and metabolome data through multi-layered network analysis. It enables network construction and advanced analyses, including hub identification, pathfinding, and node prioritization, to uncover context-specific biological associations.
